  body.grey.lighten-4
    .skewed-bg
      header.container
        a href="#"
          #logo-anim
            .planet
            .orbit
              .moon
          #logo.valign-wrapper
            object data="img/logo.svg" type="image/svg+xml" width="180" height="100"
              img.responsive-img.valign src="img/logo.png"
        #signin.valign-wrapper
          img.responsive-img.circle src="http://adriel.cafe/img/adriel_cafe.jpg"
          p
            b.white-text Adriel Café
            br
            a href="#" Sign Out
    
    main.container
      .row.grey.lighten-4
        .col.s12
  	      ul.tabs
  	        li.tab.col.s3
              a.active href="#translate" Translate
  	        li.tab.col.s3
              a href="#profile" Profile
      .row.grey.lighten-4
        == Slim::Template.new('slim/translate.slim').render()
        == Slim::Template.new('slim/profile.slim').render()
    
    #fab-add.fixed-action-btn.horizontal
      a.btn-floating.btn-large
        i.material-icons.large add
        
    footer.page-footer
      .container
        .row
          .col.l3.m6
            h5.white-text
              i.material-icons.small info
              |  About
            p.grey-text.text-lighten-4
              | NMS αβ (pronounced "alphabet") is an unofficial translation service of alien words for <a href="http://no-mans-sky.com">No Man's Sky</a>.
            p.grey-text.text-lighten-4
              | It is available for <a href="#">Web</a> and <a href="#">Android</a>.
          .col.l4.m12.offset-l1
            h5.white-text
              i.material-icons.small android
              |  Android App
            .plyr
                .responsive-video data-video-id="N6f3i4qrlbY" data-type="youtube"
            #google-play-logo.center-align
              a href="#" target="_blank"
                img.responsive-img src="img/google-play.png"
          .col.l3.m6.offset-l1
            h5.white-text
              i.material-icons.small mail
              |  Contact
            p.grey-text.text-lighten-4
              | From press? Need help? Have a question? Get in touch!
            a.btn.waves-effect.waves-light href="mailto:me@adriel.cafe" target="_blank" Email Me
